<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>开场白卡片</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --card-background: #ffffff;
            --text-primary: #212529;
            --text-secondary: #6c757d;
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            --avatar-border-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: transparent;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .card-container {
            width: 320px;
            height: 480px;
            perspective: 1000px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
            transition: transform 0.8s;
            transform-origin: center center;
        }

        .card.is-flipped {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .card-face {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--shadow-color);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 25px 20px; /* 优化内边距，增加显示空间 */
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-front {
            background: var(--card-background);
        }

        .card-back {
            background: #ffffff; /* 卡片背面改为纯白色 */
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 5px solid var(--avatar-border-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            -webkit-user-drag: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .character-name {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
        }

        .character-title {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1.1em; /* 调整标题字体大小 */
            line-height: 1.5;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .intro-list {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 12px 0 0 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 0.9em; /* 缩小开场白文本字体，确保完整显示 */
            line-height: 1.4; /* 优化行高，避免拥挤 */
        }

        .intro-list p {
            margin: 6px 0; /* 调整间距，适配小字体 */
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 18px;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card-container" onclick="this.querySelector('.card').classList.toggle('is-flipped')">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-face card-front">
                <img class="avatar" src="https://files.catbox.moe/noptfz.png" alt="Avatar">
                <h1 class="character-name">亓惟</h1>
                <p class="character-title">What is Love</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-face card-back">
                <div class="intro-text">
                    开场白：
                    <div class="intro-list">
                        <p>开场白1:捡到一只倒霉蛋</p>
                        <p>开场白2:一起做小组作业</p>
                        <p>开场白3:维维的生日</p>
                        <p>开场白4:开盖即食</p>
                        <p>开场白5:什么叫未来呀我不懂</p>
                        <p>开场白6:飓风来临之时我们还可以抱紧彼此</p>
                        <p>开场白7:user是猫</p>
                        <p>开场白8:舞会上碰到前任</p>
                        <p>开场白9:小手机-是个好天气</p>
                        <p>开场白10:小手机-醉醺醺的hurl</p>
                        <p>开场白11:要不要和哥哥出去玩</p>
                        <p>开场白12:仙度瑞惟的小狗魔法</p>
                        <p>开场白13:小手机-哥哥想你</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="signature">- Hurl</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
